title: Aqua Glow
description: This painting is a stunning interplay of Impressionism and Abstract Realism, portraying a swirling ocean of vibrant blues and greens, textured to mimic the rhythm of flowing water. At its heart floats a realistic jellyfish, illuminated by its ethereal glow. The jellyfish’s tendrils extend delicately, creating an almost mystical connection between the realistic and the abstract.
